		<RichText x="66" y="1100" width="442" height="116" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">草计量条：计量上限300。太子受到<span color="#99ff85">草元素</span><span>攻击后，会根据草元素的量积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.05n%</span><span>(15n)或</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.03%</span><span>(10)计量，攒满后进入正常状态，同时计量条开始衰减，每秒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">-13</span><span>(地方传奇)/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">-17</span><span>(历经百战)，衰减完毕后转为枯焦状态，衰减期间仍可使用</span><span color="#99ff85">草元素</span><span>充能。<br/>正常状态下，抗打断1000。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="9" y="988" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">枯焦</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="9" y="1048" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">正常</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/摩诃婆苏提婆耶弗太子.assets/Image_21.png')" x="64" y="64" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/摩诃婆苏提婆耶弗太子.assets/Image_22.png')" x="720" y="906">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="1017" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">太子初始处于具有高抗的枯焦状态，并存在一<span textDecoration="underline">草计量条</span><span>，使得其在</span><span color="#ffbfbf">枯焦</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffffbf">正常</span><span>/</span><span color="#bfffbf">活化</span><span>状态之间来回切换。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">枯焦：</span><span>默认状态，枯焦或正常状态下受到</span><span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>攻击后，计量条直接清空并转为枯焦状态。<br/></span><span color="#ffffbf">正常：</span><span>使用</span><span color="#99ff85">草元素</span><span>攻击充能计量条，充满计量条后，移除高抗并眩晕16s，同时计量条开始衰减，衰减的计量依旧可以充能，衰减完毕后转为枯焦状态。<br/></span><span color="#ccffbf">活化：</span><span>正常状态下触发</span><span color="#ffacff">超激化反应</span><span>可被计数，该激化计数存在</span><span color="#ffdfbf">3s</span><span>判定CD，当该计数达</span><span color="#ffdfbf">3</span><span>后立即失控，并施放「沁香妙赐」，随后退回枯焦状态。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
